'''Nidal Čelik''' ({{IPA|bs|nǐdal tʃělik|pron}}; born 17 July 2006) is a Bosnian professional [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Defender (association football)#Centre-back|centre-back]] for [[Ligue 1]] club [[RC Lens|Lens]] and the [[Bosnia and Herzegovina national football team|Bosnia and Herzegovina national team]].

Čelik started his professional career at [[FK Sarajevo|Sarajevo]], before joining Lens in 2025.

A former youth international for Bosnia and Herzegovina, Čelik made his senior international debut in 2025.

==Club career==

===Sarajevo===
Čelik came through the youth academy of his hometown club [[FK Sarajevo Youth School|Sarajevo]], which he joined in 2017. In July 2022, he signed his first professional contract with the team.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://faktor.ba/sport/fudbal/petnaestogodisnjak-potpisao-profesionalni-ugovor-sa-sarajevom/129108|title=Petnaestogodišnjak potpisao profesionalni ugovor sa Sarajevom|website=faktor.ba|date=8 July 2022|access-date=8 July 2022|language=bs}}</ref> He made his professional debut in a [[2023–24 Bosnia and Herzegovina Football Cup#First round|Bosnian Cup]] game against [[HNK Sloga Uskoplje|Sloga Uskoplje]] on 27 September 2023 at the age of 17.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://klix.ba/sport/nogomet/sarajevo-rutinski-pobijedilo-slogu-u-gornjem-vakufu-i-plasiralo-se-medju-16-ekipa-u-kupu-bih/230927128|title=Sarajevo rutinski pobijedilo Slogu u Gornjem Vakufu i plasiralo se među 16 ekipa u Kupu BiH|website=klix.ba|date=27 September 2023|access-date=28 September 2023|language=bs}}</ref> Two months later, he made his league debut against [[NK GOŠK Gabela|GOŠK Gabela]].<ref>{{cite news|url=https://sportsport.ba/fudbal/sarajevo-s-tri-gola-pocastilo-gosk-bordo-tim-preskocio-zrinjski-na-tabeli/464304|title=Sarajevo s tri gola počastilo GOŠK: Bordo tim preskočio Zrinjski na tabeli|website=sportsport.ba|date=9 December 2023|access-date=12 December 2023|language=bs}}</ref>

He signed a new three-year deal with the side in June 2024.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://scsport.ba/nidal-celik-produzio-ugovor-do-2027-godine|title=Nidal Čelik produžio ugovor do 2027. godine|website=scsport.ba|date=29 June 2024|access-date=1 July 2024|language=bs}}</ref>

In November, he was named squad [[Captain (association football)|captain]].<ref>{{cite news|url=https://avaz.ba/sport/nogomet/937366/sarajevo-ima-novog-kapitena-objavljen-snimak-reakcije-igraca-kada-im-je-zekic-saopcio-odluku|title=Sarajevo ima novog kapitena, objavljen snimak reakcije igrača kada im je Zekić saopćio odluku|website=avaz.ba|date=1 November 2024|access-date=1 November 2024|language=bs}}</ref>

===Lens===
In February 2025, Čelik moved to French outfit [[RC Lens|Lens]] on a contract until June 2029.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://klix.ba/sport/nogomet/nidal-celik-ostvario-najveci-transfer-u-historiji-bh-lige-i-presao-u-lens-za-25-miliona-eura/250202051|title=Nidal Čelik ostvario najveći transfer u historiji bh. lige i prešao u Lens za 2,5 miliona eura|website=klix.ba|date=3 February 2025|access-date=4 February 2025|language=bs}}</ref> On 14 February 2026, he made his official debut for the team against [[Paris FC]].<ref>{{cite news|url=https://oslobodjenje.ba/sport/fudbal/ino-fudbal/ligue-1/nidal-celik-fenomenalnim-potezom-iznenadio-i-komentatora-arena-sport-kakva-hladnokrvnost-1113481|title=Nidal Čelik fenomenalnim potezom iznenadio i komentatora Arene Sport: Kakva hladnokrvnost|website=oslobodjenje.ba|date=14 February 2026|access-date=16 February 2026|language=bs}}</ref> He won his first trophy with the club on 22 May, by beating [[Lille OSC|Lille]] in the [[2025–26 Coupe de France|Coupe de France]] final.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://n1info.ba/sport/nogomet/nidal-celik-ce-u-sjajnom-raspolozenju-stici-na-okupljanje-lens-srusio-nicu-i-osvojio-kup-francuske-fotovideo|title=Nidal Čelik će u sjajnom raspoloženju stići na okupljanje: Lens srušio Nicu i osvojio Kup Francuske|website=n1info.ba|date=22 May 2026|access-date=24 May 2026|language=bs}}</ref>

==International career==
Čelik represented [[Bosnia and Herzegovina national football team|Bosnia and Herzegovina]] at all youth levels.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://reprezentacija.ba/446420-kapiten-sarajeva-je-najmladji-zmaj-dijeliti-svlacionicu-sa-ovim-igracima-je-ostvarenje-sna|title=Kapiten Sarajeva je najmlađi Zmaj: Dijeliti svlačionicu sa ovim igračima je ostvarenje sna|website=reprezentacija.ba|date=14 November 2024|access-date=16 November 2024|language=bs}}</ref>

In November 2024, he received his first senior call up, for [[2024–25 UEFA Nations League A#Group 3|2024–25 UEFA Nations League A]] games against [[Germany national football team|Germany]] and the [[Netherlands national football team|Netherlands]],<ref>{{cite news|url=https://n1info.ba/sport/nogomet/selektor-barbarez-uputio-nove-pozive-u-reprezentaciju-bih-zamijenit-ce-povrijedjene-kolasinca-i-radeljica|title=Selektor Barbarez uputio nove pozive u reprezentaciju BiH, zamijenit će povrijeđene Kolašinca i Radeljića|website=n1info.ba|date=9 November 2024|access-date=12 November 2024|language=bs}}</ref> but had to wait until 29 May 2026 to make his debut in a [[Exhibition game#Association football|friendly]] game against [[North Macedonia national football team|North Macedonia]].<ref>{{cite news|url=https://oslobodjenje.ba/sport/fudbal/reprezentacija/foto-sergej-barbarez-podijelio-minutazu-reprezentativcima-remi-na-kosevu|title=Sergej Barbarez podijelio minutažu reprezentativcima, remi na Koševu|website=oslobodjenje.ba|date=29 May 2026|access-date=1 June 2026|language=bs}}</ref>

In June 2026, Čelik was named in Bosnia and Herzegovina's squad for the [[2026 FIFA World Cup]].<ref>{{cite news|url=https://sportske.ba/clanak/barbarez-poslao-konacan-spisak-fifa-i-jedno-ime-otputovalo-u-ameriku-ali-nije-na-listi|title=Barbarez poslao konačan spisak FIFA-i: Jedno ime otputovalo u Ameriku, ali nije na listi|website=sportske.ba|date=3 June 2026|access-date=3 June 2026|language=bs}}</ref>

